name: Dice Roller
summary:
Shake Some Dice & Enjoy the Beach!
As the sun slowly sets and the comfortable sea breeze blows over your body on the Gold Coast, you wear a sexy bikini, bathing in the lazy sunshine. Light music reaches your ear from a pub while your friends and you play the world-famous dice game. The ice in the whisky on your left hand is gradually melting away while the dice are flying in the hot air as you shake the cup with ardent passion.
